			<p class="benefit">The above is a quote from one of our brides remembering a wedding invitation she'd once received: the memory of that invitation haunted her, and she vowed never to make the same mistakes!</p>

		<p class="benefit">Yet when planning a wedding, it's easy to underestimate the important role your invitations play, not just in how they look but what they do:</p>

		<p class="benefit">They're just as important as the photographs and the dress when it comes to a record of your special day.

