<p class="benefit">First there's the matching envelopes individually handcrafted just for your order&mdash;and when I say matching, I don't just mean the colour of the envelope: each envelope is fully printed inside and out with the same design as your invitations, making them stand out from the sea of standard plain white envelopes that hold most other designs. </p>

<p class="benefit">Inside you'll find an invitation dressed in one of a range of embellishments to add that wow factor:</p>

<p class="benefit">Whether it's uwrapping the paper sleeve adorned with your monogram, unbuckling the gently glinting diamante ribbon or untying the bow, your guests will feel like they're discovering something really special. </p>


				<div style="text-align:center;">
